<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.4.4">
<l>cātimā ṇikka meṉkō cavikōḷpoṉ mutta meṉkō</l>
<l>cātinal vayira meṉkō tavivilcīr viḷakka meṉkō</l>
<l>vātiyañ cōti yeṉkō vātiyam puruṭa ṉeṉkō</l>
<l>vātumil kālat tentai yaccuta ṉamala ṉaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Will I say “ruby by kind”? Will I say “splendid gold [and] pearls”?</l>
<l>Will I say “good diamond by kind”? Will I say “lamp of unceasing excellence”?</l>
<l>Will I say “primordial light”? Will I say “primordial man”?</l>
<l>– to our father in a time without all that,  to the unshakable one, the spotless one.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
